k Maxwell Prize in Plasma Physics of the American Physical Society [120]<br />\nIEEE Maxwell Award<br />\nMaxwell Montes, a mountain range on Venus[121]<br />\nThe Maxwell Gap in the Rings of Saturn[122]<br />\nThe James Clerk Maxwell Telescope, the largest submillimetre-wavelength astronomical telescope in the world, with a diameter of 15 metres (49 ft) ][123]<br />\nThe James Clerk Maxwell Building of the University of Edinburgh, housing the schools of mathematics, physics and meteorology[124]<br />\nThe James Clerk Maxwell building at the Waterloo campus of King's College London, a chair in Physics, and a society for undergraduate physicists are named after him at the university.[125]<br />\nThe James Clerk Maxwell Science Centre of the Edinburgh Academy[126]<br />\nThe Maxwell Centre at the University of Cambridge, dedicated to academia-industry interactions in Physical Sciences and Technology.[127]<br />\nA statue on Edinburgh's George Street[128]<br />\nGPU manufacturer Nvidia has named the architecture of its GeForce 900 series after Maxwell[129]<br />\nA proposed sculpture called the Star of Caledonia is to pay tribute to James Clerk Maxwell<br />\nANSYS software for electromagnetic analysis, named Maxwell<br />\n<br />\nHonours<br />\nClub<br />\nCruzeiro<br />\nCopa do Brasil (1): 2000<br />\nAjax[28][29]<br />\nEredivisie (2): 2001&ndash;02, 2003&ndash;04<br />\nKNVB Cup (1): 2001&ndash;02<br />\nJohan Cruyff Shield (1): 2002<br />\nInternazionale[28][29]<br />\nSerie A (3): 2006&ndash;07, 2007&ndash;08, 2008&ndash;09<br />\nSupercoppa Italiana (2): 2006, 2008<br />\nBarcelona[28][29]<br />\nLa Liga (2): 2009&ndash;10, 2010&ndash;11<br />\nCopa del Rey (1): 2011&ndash;12<br />\nSupercopa de Espa&ntilde;a (2): 2009, 2010<br />\nUEFA Champions League (1): 2010&ndash;11<br />\nUEFA Super Cup (1): 2009<br />\nFIFA Club World Cup (2): 2009, 2011<br />\nParis Saint-Germain[28][29]<br />\nLigue 1 (4): 2012&ndash;13, 2013&ndash;14, 2014&ndash;15, 2015&ndash;16<br />\nCoupe de France (3): 2014&ndash;15, 2015&ndash;16, 2016&ndash;17<br />\nCoupe de la Ligue (4): 2013&ndash;14, 2014&ndash;15, 2015&ndash;16, 2016&ndash;17<br />\nTroph&eacute;e des Champions (3): 2013, 2015, 2016<br />\nIndividual<br />\nDutch Footballer of the Year (1): 2003&ndash;04<br />\nDutch Golden Shoe (1): 2003&ndash;04<br />\nLigue 1 Team of the Year (3): 2012&ndash;13, 2014&ndash;15, 2015&ndash;16"},{"pid":"d54dd5e8021e8172e71a11982140808edb448bc6","tid":913462,"uid":205143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T14:20:23.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以講下佢做咗咩，點解一直有人追擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"255e791eda7380da6017c4f95b7dc3c16507caad","tid":913462,"uid":141442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d54dd5e8021e8172e71a11982140808edb448bc6","tid":913462,"uid":205143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T14:20:23.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以講下佢做咗咩，點解一直有人追擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T17:30:49.000Z","msg":"同問"},{"pid":"d4ae284d5500a4dce6dd5c3f1d639c854ce635e1","tid":913462,"uid":135786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T17:47:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2855513742ef4b4a201847adf9726ca019c008d1","tid":913462,"uid":152520,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"255e791eda7380da6017c4f95b7dc3c16507caad","tid":913462,"uid":141442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d54dd5e8021e8172e71a11982140808edb448bc6","tid":913462,"uid":205143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T14:20:23.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以講下佢做咗咩，點解一直有人追擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T17:30:49.000Z","msg":"同問"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T02:21:10.000Z","msg":"佢呢排低調咗啲，佢以前日日上黎撩事鬥非，唔係假膠嗰隻，係整晒圖表搵晒資料黎插人地間學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />